    "text": "The lethargy is horrific and nobody understands how hard it is to deal with. People see it as me \"napping\" all the time, it's involuntary, once that wall hits, it's time out, I have no choice, and because endo is invisible, everyone thinks there's nothing wrong with me and no reason for it.",
