  {
    "cid": "7650251469271466774",
    "text": "Fatigue was one of the worst symptoms for me, you feel like you are letting people down and people think you’re lazy. The pain is an obvious symptom but fatigue was put down to so many other issues it was really difficult to know that it was endo causing it. Anyway, after laparoscopy and the coil and a different diet, I’m feeling much better and getting to exercise and do the things I love. Don’t give up ladies xxx",
    "digg_count": 22,
    "reply_comment_total": 0,
