      "primary_emotion": "neutral",
      "toxicity_spam_flag": false
    }
  },
  {
    "cid": "7650017234944951062",
    "text": "It’s one of my worst symptoms and so debilitating. I developed endo later in life. And used to be someone who could survive of 3 hours of sleep. Now I have this condition along with insomnia and lethargy. It’s so debilitating. I was so active and now the thought of leaving the house seems too exhausting 😫",
    "digg_count": 14,
    "reply_comment_total": 0,
